    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos vir
                        gloriosissimus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/111">Aio</persName>
                        Dei previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, per
                            <rs key="#Intercessory">rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/112" key="#Intercessory">Ladelchis</persName> dilecti
                        germani nostri, tibi <persName key="#Other_palatine_officer #Prevosts"
                            ref="#people/113">Criscio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">medico</rs> nostro atque <rs
                            key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs> ad parte <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Property_of_persons_without_heirs #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancii Benedicati</orgName> quod situm est
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/109">Monte
                        Casino</placeName>, h[ob] anime nostre salute, hec est <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Property_of_persons_without_heirs #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >omnibus rebus omnibusque pertinentiis quibus fuit <persName
                                ref="#people/116"
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                                >Potoni</persName> filii <persName><name ref="Potitius"
                                    >Potitionis</name></persName> infra <rs key="#Fines"
                                >finibus</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/112" key="#Fines">Alifanis</placeName> et
                                <placeName ref="#places/111" key="#Fines"
                        >Telesinis</placeName></rs>, pro quo ipse Poto in anima domini <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115">Adelchis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs> dilectissimi genitori nostro consiliatus
                        fuit eumque interfecit, et legibus omnibus eius rebus et facultatibus nostre
                        hevenit potestati, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum <rs key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum</rs>
                        siperius dictis omnibus rebus hac pertinentiis eodem Sancti Benedicti
                        cenobio eiusque rectores habere et possidere valeas, et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        prephato monasterio habeas aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus
                        possideas. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione suprascriptac
                        potestatis scripsi ego locus sigilli <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actumd <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110"><rs key="#Cities">Beneventi</rs>
                        </placeName><date>primo anno, mense Maio, tertia indictione</date>.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
